snippet.title: The Witness first official gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
This is the first official trailer for The Witness, to be released on the PC, iOS, and PlayStation 4... and eventually, several other platforms.     ESRB Rating: EVERYONE with Alcohol Reference.
The music is "Glass Window", composed by Cylindra Sapphire of Mediaeval Baebes.

Front page for the game: http://the-witness.net/

Follow development on the game's blog: http://the-witness.net/news/

The music is "Glass Window" by the Mediaeval Baebes. Used by permission. 

http://www.amazon.com/Glass-Window/dp/B004947UV0/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&qid=1361468909&sr=8-2&keywords=medi%C3%A6val+b%C3%A6bes+glass+window
